title: Agentic Machine Learning Engineer Inspired by Karpathy
description: A new GitHub project creates an 'agentic Machine Learning Engineer' that trains state-of-the-art ML models using Claude Code SDK and Google ADK. This project embodies Karpathy's recent emphasis on AI-native development approaches and his concept of Software 3.0.
author: K-Dense-AI

title: AI for Data Engineers - Simon Willison Podcast Discussion
description: Simon Willison appeared on the Talking Postgres podcast discussing AI applications for data engineers. The conversation covered practical AI tools and workflows for data engineering tasks.

title: AI Agents in Data Journalism - Simon Willison

author: Simon Willison

title: AI Coworkers: The Future of Development Teams

description: A comprehensive academic survey examining LLM-based agents that autonomously perform software development tasks. The paper analyzes current techniques and methodologies in AI-driven programming.
author: Research Paper
